@startuml
left to right direction
actor "采购商" as Buyer
actor "供应商" as Supplier

rectangle "系统" {
    usecase "下单" as PlaceOrder
    usecase "付款" as MakePayment
    usecase "订单跟踪" as TrackOrder
    usecase "确认收货" as ConfirmReceipt
    usecase "查看交易记录" as ViewTransactionRecords
    usecase "交易评价" as TradeEvaluation
}

Buyer --> PlaceOrder : 选择产品及数量生成订单并提交
PlaceOrder --> System : 存储订单信息，进入后续流程

Buyer --> MakePayment : 选择支付方式完成付款
MakePayment --> System : 更新订单状态，通知供应商发货
Supplier --> MakePayment : 获取发货通知

Buyer --> TrackOrder : 查看订单状态和进度
Supplier --> TrackOrder : 查看订单状态和进度
TrackOrder --> System : 获取实时订单状态信息

Buyer --> ConfirmReceipt : 确认收到货物
ConfirmReceipt --> System : 更新订单状态

Buyer --> ViewTransactionRecords : 查看历史订单信息
Supplier --> ViewTransactionRecords : 查看历史订单信息
ViewTransactionRecords --> System : 查询数据库并展示

Buyer --> TradeEvaluation : 对交易进行评价
Supplier --> TradeEvaluation : 对交易进行评价
TradeEvaluation --> System : 展示评价结果在企业信息页面
@enduml